This Agreement governs the use of Software Mansion S.A. software suite which encompasses two distinct processing capabilities:

1. Offline Processing: This includes any non-real-time data processing, batch processing, or processing of pre-recorded content. This use case is governed by the license terms detailed below, analogous to the permissive MIT license.

2. Real-time Processing (Smelter): This includes any live streaming, real-time content processing, or interactive media handling. This use case is subject to specific usage limitations and commercial terms outlined in this Agreement.

Software Mansion S.A. ("Licensor") provides this software and associated documentation files (the "Software") to the organization licensing the Software ("Organization"), including all its affiliates and subsidiaries. Any unique end user receiving content processed by the Software is considered a "Viewer" under this Agreement.

